examples.en: She failed to heed the warnings.
Our warnings did not dissuade them.
We took Stephen's warnings to heart.
Warnings of disaster may be overblown.
Several earlier studies had sounded similar warnings.
His warnings are echoed by many other experts in the field.
Despite repeated warnings, they have continued to flout the law.
If she had only heeded my warnings, none of this would have happened.
These warnings have been heard so often that they have lost their impact.
Ignoring the avalanche warnings, the fatuous skiers continued on their course.
